<refnamediv>
<refname><systemitem>display-aa</systemitem></refname>
<refpurpose>Display using AAlib</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<cmdsynopsis>
<command>display-aalib</command>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>

<para>Uses the <ulink url="http://aa-project.sourceforge.net/aalib/">AA-lib</ulink>, 
an ASCII art library, for output and input.</para>
  
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>Environment variables</title>
<para>
AA-lib options may be specified using the the <envar>AA_OPTS</envar> variable.
</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>Features</title>

<simplelist>
<member>DirectBuffer always available</member>
<member>Unaccelerated</member>
<member>Currently, only supports 8-bit palettized modes</member>
</simplelist>

</refsect1>

</refentry>
